  "content": {
    "raw": "<!-- wp:flatsome/uxbuilder -->\n[section bg=\"496\" bg_size=\"original\" bg_overlay=\"rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.68)\" padding=\"70px\"]\n\n[row style=\"collapse\"]\n\n[col span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"1.7\" text_align=\"center\" text_color=\"rgb(19, 19, 19)\"]\n\n<h2>Web Hosting</h2>\n\n[/ux_text]\n[ux_text font_size=\"1.2\" text_align=\"center\" text_color=\"rgb(19, 19, 19)\"]\n\n<p>Experience seamless online presence with our Reliable Web Hosting Solutions. Our cutting-edge hosting services ensure that your website operates smoothly, loading quickly and securely for visitors around the clock. With top-tier data centers, advanced security measures, and 24/7 technical support, we provide the foundation for your digital success. Choose from a range of hosting options tailored to your needs, whether you're a small business, a growing e-commerce store, or a dynamic corporate entity. Trust us to keep your website accessible and responsive, so you can focus on what matters most – your content and customers.</p>\n\n[/ux_text]\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n\n[/section]\n[row h_align=\"center\"]\n\n[col span=\"8\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"1.25\" text_align=\"center\" text_color=\"rgb(0,0,0)\"]\n\n<p>Our Featured Plans 5GB SSD Cloud Storage Unlimited Premium Bandwidth 200% CPU Allowance 2GB Memory Allowance 15GB SSD Cloud Storage Unlimited Premium Bandwidth 300% CPU Allowance</p>\n<div class=\"product-shared-hosting-price-item__features-item clearfix\">\n<div class=\"product-shared-hosting-price-item__features-item-text product-shared-hosting-price-item__features-item-text--dashed\">6GB Memory Allowance</div>\n</div>\n<p>25GB SSD Cloud Storage Unlimited Premium Bandwidth 400% CPU Allowance 8GB Memory Allowance</p>\n[/ux_text]\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n[row]\n\n[col span__sm=\"12\" align=\"center\"]\n\n[button text=\"Contact us\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n\n<!-- /wp:flatsome/uxbuilder -->\n\n[section padding=\"60px\" bg_color=\"rgb(243, 243, 243)\"]\n  [row]\n    [col span__sm=\"12\"]\n      [ux_text]\n        <!-- AI_SLOT:INTRO -->\n        <p><strong>Web Hosting</strong> built for speed and reliability, with support when you need it. Ideal for Newcastle small business sites.</p>\n        <!-- /AI_SLOT:INTRO -->\n\n        <!-- AI_SLOT:FAQ -->\n        <h2>Hosting FAQ</h2>\n        <h3>Can you migrate my existing website?</h3>\n        <p>Yes. We can help move your site with minimal downtime.</p>\n        <h3>Do you provide backups and security?</h3>\n        <p>We focus on secure hosting, updates, and best-practice hardening depending on your plan.</p>\n        <h3>Is email included?</h3>\n        <p>It depends on your setup. We can recommend the best option for your business email.</p>\n        <h3>What support do you offer?</h3>\n        <p>We provide technical support and can offer ongoing maintenance packages.</p>\n        <!-- /AI_SLOT:FAQ -->\n\n        <!-- AI_SLOT:CTA -->\n<h2>Choose a hosting plan</h2>\n        <p><a class=\"button primary is-large\" href=\"https://newcastlehub.info/contact/\">Ask about hosting</a></p>\n        <p>Related: <a href=\"https://newcastlehub.info/website-service/\">Website Service</a> | <a href=\"https://newcastlehub.info/marketing-service/\">Digital Marketing</a></p>\n<p>Related reads: <a href=\"https://newcastlehub.info/newcastle-growth-hub/\">Newcastle Growth Hub</a> | <a href=\"https://newcastlehub.info/web-hosting-starter/\">Web Hosting Starter</a> | <a href=\"https://newcastlehub.info/web-hosting-freedom/\">Web Hosting Freedom</a></p>\n<p>Related reads: <a href=\"https://newcastlehub.info/web-hosting-premier/\">Web Hosting Premier</a> | <a href=\"https://newcastlehub.info/hosting-plan/\">Hosting Plan Overview</a></p>\n<p>Related reads: <a href=\"https://newcastlehub.info/ecommerce-setup-newcastle/\">Ecommerce Setup Newcastle</a> | <a href=\"https://newcastlehub.info/booking-system-newcastle/\">Booking System Setup Newcastle</a> | <a href=\"https://newcastlehub.info/free-newcastle-business-audit/\">Free Newcastle Business Audit</a></p>\n<!-- /AI_SLOT:CTA -->\n\n        <!-- AI_SLOT:SCHEMA -->\n        <script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Can you migrate my existing website?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes. We can help move your site with minimal downtime.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Do you provide backups and security?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"We focus on secure hosting, updates, and best-practice hardening depending on your plan.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Is email included?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"It depends on your setup. We can recommend the best option for your business email.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What support do you offer?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"We provide technical support and can offer ongoing maintenance packages.\"}}]}</script>\n        <!-- /AI_SLOT:SCHEMA -->\n      [/ux_text]\n    [/col]\n  [/row]\n[/section]\n",
